Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\bord2\blur0.7\3c&333333\4c&333333}那你们给我办事 当做交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\bord2\blur0.7\3c&333333\4c&333333}なら　依頼と交換条件といこうか
