Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&FFE6D6\bord2\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}報酬はそれで十分すぎるさ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&FFE6D6\bord2\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}我看起来落寞吗
